snippet.title: Amberlynn Reid Has Been Through Her Grapevine of Therapists
snippet.description:
...or - how Our Gorl still manages to stay cool, calm and collective despite all the crulety she has to endure, leaving her feeling like she's stuck in a rock and a hard place, all while battling both acid reflex, sailmonelia and a very badly case of cagening unsomnia.

And all Our Gorl wants is to sit on Hawaii.
